  <li>Operational Time:
    <ul>
      <li>3hrs typ/8hrs max</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Power:
    <ul>
      <li>1000W peak</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Battery:
    <ul>
      <li>48V 20Ah Li-Po</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Maximum Permissible Gradient:
    <ul>
      <li>IP66</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Encoder:
    <ul>
      <li>25000Pulses/m</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Feedback:
